{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/yeofr\/quickstart"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]},{"paths":["\/documentation\/yeofr\/quickstart"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Get up and running with "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"YEOFR","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" in minutes."}],"kind":"article","primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"1-Add-the-SDK","text":"1. Add the SDK"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Integrate "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YEOFR.xcframework"},{"type":"text","text":" (or SPM package) into your project."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"import YEOFR","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" at the top of your Swift files.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"1a-Pilot-unlock-for-non-YEO-bundle-IDs","type":"heading","text":"1a. Pilot unlock for non-YEO bundle IDs"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"YEOFR is gated to YEO-owned apps by default — on a non-YEO bundle ID the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"process aborts the moment a ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/YEOFRSDK","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" instance is constructed, with a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"printed contact hint.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For evaluation customers, we issue a ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"temporary unlock code"}]},{"text":" that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"bypasses the bundle gate during a fixed pilot window. Email","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"christo@yeomessaging.com"}]},{"text":" to request one.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The code is passed to the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/YEOFRSDK"},{"type":"text","text":" initializer — there is no static"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"activate(...)"},{"type":"text","text":" call and no "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"shared"},{"type":"text","text":" singleton. "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Constructing the instance","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is what runs the bundle gate","type":"text"}]},{"text":", so the code must be supplied right there.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"On a non-YEO bundle ID an absent or expired code aborts at this line;","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"reaching the next line is itself proof the gate passed:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["import YEOFR","","\/\/ On a non-YEO bundle ID the gate passes only with a valid, unexpired code.","let sdk = YEOFRSDK(pilotUnlockCode: \"<contact-us-for-pilot-code>\")"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The code has a ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"hard expiry baked into the SDK build","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":". Once expired,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"no code unlocks the gate regardless of value — request a fresh build.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This is a stop-gap for the 0.5.x cycle; the forward-looking licensing","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"scheme is tracked under CSI-384.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If your app is YEO-owned, the code is optional (the gate passes natively),","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"so any value — or none — works: ","type":"text"},{"code":"let sdk = YEOFRSDK()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"2-Create-a-tracker","type":"heading","text":"2. Create a tracker"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Reuse the ","type":"text"},{"code":"sdk","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" instance you constructed in step 1a (for a YEO-owned app,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"simply ","type":"text"},{"code":"let sdk = YEOFRSDK()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"):","type":"text"}]},{"code":["_ = sdk.createTracker()"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"anchor":"2a-Check-the-framework-compatability-code","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"2a. Check the framework compatability code"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Persist the compatability code alongside enrollment data. If it changes after a framework","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"update, require the user to re-enroll before loading stored tracker data."}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["let compatabilityCode = YEOFRSDK.compatabilityCode","print(compatabilityCode) \/\/ \"A\" or \"B\""]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Objective-C callers can use the framework metadata shim:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"objc","type":"codeListing","code":["NSString *compatabilityCode = [YEOFRFrameworkMetadata compatabilityCode];"]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"3. Detect faces from a pixel buffer","anchor":"3-Detect-faces-from-a-pixel-buffer"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["import AVFoundation","","\/\/ Inside your AVCaptureVideoDataOutput callback:","let dict = sdk.detectFaces(from: pixelBuffer, needFaceRect: true)","","print(dict[\"detectedCount\"] ?? 0)   \/\/ number of faces"]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"4. Register a face","anchor":"4-Register-a-face"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Take a faceID returned from detection and give it a display name:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["if let faceIDs = dict[\"faceIDs\"] as? [[String: Any]],","   let first = faceIDs.first,","   let index = first[\"index\"] as? Int {","","    let rc = sdk.enroll(faceID: Int64(index), name: \"Alice\", learnFromCurrentFrame: true)","    print(\"Enroll result:\", rc)","}"]},{"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing","code":["•\tfaceID comes from detection results.","•\tname is any string you want to associate with that face.","•\tSet learnFromCurrentFrame to true to train from the current image."]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"5. Serialize tracker data","anchor":"5-Serialize-tracker-data"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["if let nsdata = sdk.faceRecognitionTrackerData() {","    let base64 = nsdata.base64EncodedString()","    \/\/ Save to disk or send to server","}"]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"6. Load tracker data","anchor":"6-Load-tracker-data"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["if let blob = ... as NSData {","    _ = sdk.loadTracker(from: blob)","}"]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"NOTES","anchor":"NOTES"},{"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing","code":["•\tConstruct a single `YEOFRSDK` instance and reuse it — activation runs once in its initializer.","•\t`YEOFRSDK.compatabilityCode` is the supported source of truth for enrollment compatibility checks.","•\tPublic API is Foundation-based (NSData, NSDictionary, NSString) to ensure compatibility with Objective-C and React Native.","•\tFor Swift convenience, internal helpers wrap these as Data and value types."]}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR"]]},"metadata":{"role":"article","modules":[{"name":"YEOFR"}],"roleHeading":"Article","title":"QuickStart"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/QuickStart"},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR":{"url":"\/documentation\/yeofr","title":"YEOFR","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR","abstract":[{"text":"A device-only face recognition SDK for iOS.","type":"text"}],"role":"collection","type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR/YEOFRSDK":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/yeofr\/yeofrsdk","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"YEOFRSDK","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"YEOFRSDK","abstract":[{"text":"YEOFR main entry point.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"YEOFRSDK","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/YEOFRSDK"}},"variantOverrides":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"patch":[{"path":"\/identifier\/interfaceLanguage","value":"occ","op":"replace"},{"path":"\/topicSections","value":null,"op":"add"},{"path":"\/seeAlsoSections","value":null,"op":"add"}]}]}